Package: PsyEmbedR
Title: Semantic Auditing Tools for Psychometric Item Banks
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Jose",
           family = "GM",
           email = "josegm@example.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a local workflow for preliminary semantic auditing of
    psychometric items without relying on external AI APIs. The package
    integrates R with Python through 'reticulate' and uses
    'sentence-transformers' to generate embeddings, quantify semantic
    similarity, align items to theoretical definitions, flag redundancy,
    visualize semantic maps, and summarize semantic coverage across
    dimensions.
